Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:46.41,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我祈願與你並肩前行
Comment: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:48.52,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}Beautiful it’s beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.93,0:22:53.22,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}正確與否
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:55.57,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}只取決於自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.79,0:23:03.44,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而莫衷一是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.33,0:23:10.35,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}時而詞不達意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:12.41,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}這也無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.41,0:23:15.87,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}讓弱小的我變得強大
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.87,0:23:21.42,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}是為與你相稱
