Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.90,0:23:27.90,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}我難以割捨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.90,0:23:32.39,ED_CH_EP13,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur2}亦如無法放棄
